Class UserList

  • java.lang.Object
    • acc.model.UserList

  • public class UserList
extends java.lang.Object
    The UserList class contains utility functions. It is responsible for reading data from an inFile

    Also included a method for detecting an if a string contains only integers, a method for ensuring all IDs are unique, and a method to save the contents of a list.
